  "title": "Understanding Anatomy and Proportions",
  "lessonText": "Mastering anatomy is crucial for creating believable characters.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Anatomy forms the foundation of character design.\n- Proportions vary between different character types.\n- Understanding human anatomy helps in stylizing characters.\n- Study skeletal and muscular structures for accuracy.\n- Use reference images for better understanding.\n- Practice drawing from life to improve skills."
  }
}
